quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Senin innde joom Ma ɓurnde toowde
  87,2,Oon takɗo O fonndi
  87,3,Oon koddirɗo refti O feewni
  87,4,Oon yaltinɗo durngol
  87,5,O watti ngol yoorko wayliiko
  87,6,Ma Min njanngin Ma A yeɓjjittah
  87,7,Si wonah ko Alla haaji pellet hombo anndi ko feeñi e ko wirnii
  87,8,Min newnan Ma na newori
  87,9,Siftinir ɗoon ɗo ciftanirgol na nafata
  87,10,Ma waacta oon kulɗo Alla
  87,11,Woɗɗitoo mbo ɓurɗo hiiteede
  87,12,Oon naatoowo yiite mannge nge
  87,13,Refti o maayatah toon o wuuratah
  87,14,Malaama oon laaɓɗo e sirku
  87,15,O jantii Innde joom makko o juuli
  87,16,"Ko woni, ko hoɗon ɓurna nguurndam aduna"
  87,17,Ko laakira ɓuri moƴƴude e heddaade
  87,18,ɗum ina e ɗereeji gadiiɗi
  87,19,ɗereeji Ibraahiima e Muusa